        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer197529340" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13888483289298993860">A delightful, sprightly farce infused with a buoyant energy that captures the essence of old-world Europe. The original title, &quot;The Vatican Swindle,&quot; seems more appropriate. While Lafcadio enables the crux of Gide&apos;s philosophical musings, there&apos;s much more to this story than that. Although I was interested in Gide&apos;s exploration of &quot;a crime without motive,&quot; I found his descriptions of bed bugs much more memorable and entertaining. A great book for an armchair traveler, or a backpacking/train adve</span>
  <span id="freeText13888483289298993860" style="display:none">A delightful, sprightly farce infused with a buoyant energy that captures the essence of old-world Europe. The original title, "The Vatican Swindle," seems more appropriate. While Lafcadio enables the crux of Gide's philosophical musings, there's much more to this story than that. Although I was interested in Gide's exploration of "a crime without motive," I found his descriptions of bed bugs much more memorable and entertaining. A great book for an armchair traveler, or a backpacking/train adventure in Europe. </span>
  <a data-text-id="13888483289298993860" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

