        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer152064518" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15478865606736804891">One of the finest Novels ever written. One in a cycle of Old Great Novels about &quot;Crime and Punishment&quot;, which includes Dostoevsky, Gide, Camus, and Celine, that Nazi.</span>
  <span id="freeText15478865606736804891" style="display:none">One of the finest Novels ever written. One in a cycle of Old Great Novels about "Crime and Punishment", which includes Dostoevsky, Gide, Camus, and Celine, that Nazi.</span>
