        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer117124074" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12930757170547329239">This was fun. Gide is an under-rated master of pacing and character development. The jacket copy oversells the book as some kind of proto-Camus exploration of &quot;unmotivated crime,&quot; but really it&apos;s a retro-18th-century-style farce, full of mistaken identity, improbable coincidences, estates satire, and some gleeful mockery of religion thrown in for good measure.</span>
  <span id="freeText12930757170547329239" style="display:none">This was fun. Gide is an under-rated master of pacing and character development. The jacket copy oversells the book as some kind of proto-Camus exploration of "unmotivated crime," but really it's a retro-18th-century-style farce, full of mistaken identity, improbable coincidences, estates satire, and some gleeful mockery of religion thrown in for good measure.</span>
  <a data-text-id="12930757170547329239" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
